$ LibreOffice Calc: Tools -> Options | Language Settings -> Languages

Language of:
  • User interface

Formats:
  • Locale settings
  • Default currency
  • Decimal separator key
  • Date acceptance patterns

Default Language for Documents:
  • Western
  • [] Asian
  • [] Complex text layout (with the option to set it *for current document only*).

Enhanced Language Support
  • Ignore system input language

